Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:04.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:06.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From one fierce battle after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:10.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,we Alliance members had finally defeated \Nall the members of Oracion Seis!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:17.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that triggered the seal on Brain's \Nalternate personality, Master Zero, to unlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder for how long...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:02:02.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will I be able to remain \Nanchored at this harbor known as battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:10.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:20.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe? I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:21.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... He forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:42.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal's memories are all \Njumbled up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:48.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem to remember about you, or me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:51.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Then that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Pegasus to the Fairies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy Marvel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:15.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:22.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tell me you've also \Nforgotten how to stop Nirvana...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:34.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A self-destruct magic circle \Nwill no longer work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:37.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know of any other way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:39.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what is going to happen to our guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:52.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't stop it soon, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:54.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:39.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so afraid of? This is our fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:44.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabula! Punishment for our great sin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:57.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone should just be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:02.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Caitshelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... This \Nlight... This magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana is going to fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:16.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:44.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! Men-men-men-men-men...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:07.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana's leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:19.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:31.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magical bomber, Christina!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on our side?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:37.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody... Somebody, respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are safe, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:43.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice... Is that you, Hibiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:45.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're safe too, I see, Wendy-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:51.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'm safe as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai! Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:57.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? I thought \NChristina was shot down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was shot out of the sky like nothing by \Nthose guys near the entrance to the Woodsea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it could still fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... We managed, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:13.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just a temporary alliance, so \Nteamwork is all the more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:20.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lyon is using his Creation magic to replace \Nthe wing that was destroyed from their attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:23.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The hull, which was split into pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:31.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is being held together by Sherry-san's \NDoll Attack and Ren's Air Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:36.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never manipulated something so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:39.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You call this h-heavy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:43.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The attack from before was Eve's Snow Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:51.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I fused together the magic bombs \Nthat Christina had on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:56.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but all we could take out was one leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:08:00.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... just that sturdy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:07.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And... now... my magic power is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:08.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eve, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not doing so well over here, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:18.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! A little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:35.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can hear, we're reaching \Nthe limit of our magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't attack from the ship any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:44.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know how long we'll \Nbe able to stay in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to this, before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:55.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It took a long time, but I finally \Nfound it inside the Archive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to stop Nirvana!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:02.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:07.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana has six leg-looking things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:13.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're actually more like pipes that suck \Nup magic energy from the earth itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:20.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lacrima that regulate that absorption \Nare located where the 6 legs join the main body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:26.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you destroy those 6 lacrima in \Ndifferent locations at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana will be completely deactivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One at a time won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The other lacrima will regenerate \Nthe one that was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:39.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy six lacrima in different \Nplaces simultaneously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:40.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:44.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to coordinate the timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:49.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think I can keep \Nthe telepathy up that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:58.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've uploaded the timing to your brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,20 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.06,0:10:05.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nirvana is almost ready to fire again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Six lacrima...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:09.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know you all can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:16.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:20.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:21.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the guy called Brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's jacked my telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:28.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:32.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero... The Master of Oracion Seis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oracian Seis's master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:40.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let me praise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:46.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought there would be someone \Nwho could use Archive like Brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.98,0:10:52.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So he knew about Nirvana \Nbecause of his Archive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, wizards of the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:10:59.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting now, I will destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a start, I have destroyed \Nthree of your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dragon Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:09.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An Ice Creation Wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Celestial Spirit Wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe some cat, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and the others are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's got to be a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:22.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you said something about \Ndestroying the lacrima at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:30.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I am standing in front \Nof one of those six lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:39.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I am here, destroying all \Nsix at the same time is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero has cut off his transmission...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:49.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we are going to destroy \Nall six at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:55.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,then we have no choice but to split \Nup and each head to a different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The chances of encountering Zero are 1 in 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:05.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's more, unless it's you, Erza, \Nthere's no chance of winning against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! What are you even saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have six people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:12.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have six wizards that \Ncould destroy the lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't use any...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...magic that can destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:22.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have two here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no one else that can move?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I not still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I am tied up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:41.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:45.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes... three.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:50.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh! My magic power is... My \Ntelepathy is going to run out...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:54.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We need three more! Someone answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no one else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Christina is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's losing altitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:08.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I've run out of magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:10.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:17.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Christina is crashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:52.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a proud disciple of Ul!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:56.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going to lose \Nto the likes of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:05.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy... I... really hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:11.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just 'cause you're a little \Ncute, you think you're all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:16.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're stupid \Nand clumsy and a weakling...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:20.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But how can I hate you if you die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't feel right... So answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:32.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:34.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He-cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:36.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear our voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:54.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We... can... hear you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:04.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll destroy... all \Nsix... lacrima at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:13.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:20.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And a lucky one gets to fight \NZero on the way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only 18 minutes \Nleft... We have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:28.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna protect Carla and Wendy's guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:37.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My telepathy is going to run out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:42.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have a map in \Nyour brains that I sent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:45.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I numbered each of the lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:49.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide on which one of you goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:57.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sherry... You try too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:08.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope Zero's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will head to four.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:16.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My parfum tells me that it \Nis the closest one to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:18.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The map is what told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:21.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really necessary to correct me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take five.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza! You doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:28.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Thanks to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're six.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:34.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:38.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu doesn't know about \Nyour circumstances yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:41.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks you're an enemy. Don't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:50.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The telepathy cut off...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was at his limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes six.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it sounds like we have six people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:11.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Whoever runs into Zero \Nis responsible for defeating him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has their own place \Nto go, so there's no backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:24.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! Men! Men! Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:30.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Four! I am going to four!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:34.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is counting on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:38.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot betray that trust, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to catch my breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:46.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am still young! Men! Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still alive, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you come here for, you little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:25.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be you who breaks, or me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Zero is at number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:32.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where Natsu-san is going!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a good nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He chose one for that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go and give him backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we all fight together, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:46.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything to him and we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Na...tsu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to head to our destination!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm five. You're six, Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.07,0:20:01.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:06.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:22.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu Dragneel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You move better than you did before...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Capriccio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think I'm on the same level as Brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of us will break, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be {\i1}you{\i0}, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:19.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:39.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're able to stop piercing \Nmagic... Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.47,0:22:07.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your memories return?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:24:00.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know how to stop Nirvana, \Nso it's time to cut loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.09,0:24:01.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.27,0:24:03.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone's all beat up...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:06.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody has the energy to cut loose anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where spirit kicks in!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this one time, I'm jealous \Nof your simplicity, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Power of Memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:18.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to show \NCarla how cool you can be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gettin' fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:24.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now who's the simple-minded one?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:26.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
